metadata.name: GM!LM!
metadata.description:
Sinana and White Tiger were sleeping soundly.  
It was a little cold, but the sun was shining brightly and birds were chirping.  
 Another morning has arrived.  
It's a refreshing morning. Rubbing her sleepy eyes, he looks at the white tiger still sleeping slowly.  
 It's a nice morning.

GM!LM!

シナーナ君はホワイトタイガーとともにぐっすりと眠っていた。  
少し寒さもあるけれど、明るい陽射しと鳥のさえずり。今日も朝が来た。  
さわやかな朝だ。少しばかり眠たい目をこすりながら、まだゆっくりと微睡む白いトラを見る。いい朝だ。
